item.title: Tua Tagovailoa practices for the first time since suffering a concussion in Week 2
item.description: Tua Tagovailoa practiced Wednesday for the first time since suffering a concussion in Week 2, and the Dolphins are aiming for him to start Sunday against Arizona.

item.title: More than 1,600 voters have registration revoked under Virginia program targeting noncitizens
item.description: More than 1,600 Virginians have had their voter registrations canceled since August under a state program that the Justice Department and advocacy groups contend is illegal.
